            "next": "emberfang_correct",
            "effect": { "dialogueCompleted": "npc_dialogue_trees_echo.json:emberfang_answer" }
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c2_wrong",
            "text": "A literal flame.",
            "next": "emberfang_wrong"
          }
        ]
      },
      "emberfang_correct": {
        "text": "Passion fuels the Emberfang’s legacy. Embrace its fire to inherit its strength.",
        "choices": [],
        "end": true
      },
      "emberfang_wrong": {
        "text": "No, mortal. The flame is passion, not mere fire. Try again or seek another path.",
        "choices": [
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_retry",
            "text": "Let me try again.",
            "next": "emberfang_path"
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_return",
            "text": "I’ll choose another legacy.",
            "next": "start"
          }
        ]
      },
      "mosshide_path": {
        "text": "Mosshide’s root anchors the Grove. Offer a relic of earth to prove your resolve. Do you have one?",
        "choices": [
          {
            "choiceId": "c2_offer_root",
            "text": "I offer a Mosshide Root.",
            "next": "mosshide_correct",
            "effect": { "inventoryCheck": "mosshide_root", "dialogueCompleted": "npc_dialogue_trees_echo.json:mosshide_answer" }
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c2_no_root",
            "text": "I have no relic.",
            "next": "mosshide_wrong"
          }
        ]
      },
      "mosshide_correct": {
        "text": "The root binds you to Mosshide’s legacy. Its strength is yours to inherit.",
        "choices": [],
        "end": true
      },
      "mosshide_wrong": {
        "text": "Without a relic, Mosshide’s legacy remains closed. Seek a Mosshide Root or choose another path.",
        "choices": [
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_find_root",
            "text": "I’ll find a Mosshide Root.",
            "next": null,
            "end": true
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_return",
            "text": "I’ll choose another legacy.",
            "next": "start"
          }
        ]
      },
      "cloudtail_path": {
        "text": "Cloudtail’s wind dances free. Solve this riddle: I travel unseen, yet all feel my touch. What am I?",
        "choices": [
          {
            "choiceId": "c2_wind",
            "text": "The wind.",
            "next": "cloudtail_correct",
            "effect": { "dialogueCompleted": "npc_dialogue_trees_echo.json:cloudtail_answer" }
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c2_wrong",
            "text": "A shadow.",
            "next": "cloudtail_wrong"
          }
        ]
      },
      "cloudtail_correct": {
        "text": "The wind speaks your truth! Cloudtail’s legacy of freedom is yours to claim.",
        "choices": [],
        "end": true
      },
      "cloudtail_wrong": {
        "text": "A shadow? No, it is the wind. Try again or seek another path.",
        "choices": [
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_retry",
            "text": "Let me try again.",
            "next": "cloudtail_path"
          },
          {
            "choiceId": "c3_return",
            "text": "I’ll choose another legacy.",
            "next": "start"
          }
